title: Batman vs. Predator - The Collected Edition TPB (1993|MM-Syl3ntB
description: What happens when the World's Greatest Detective meets the Universe's Greatest Hunter? well, not tea and crumpets, that's for sure. Adam and Andy Kubert illustrate these fun DC/Dark Horse crossovers that feature Batman and the Predator tangling in many different situations. All of them are violent, as you might expect. Thanks to Minutemen-Syl3ntBob for this great copy, please seed and enjoy! :-)
